eree)|Bill McCreary]]\n|\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Mike Cvik]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Antti H\u00e4m\u00e4l\u00e4inen]]\n|-\n|[[Ice hockey at the 1998 Winter Olympics \u2013 Men's tournament|1998]]<br />\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Bill McCreary (referee)|Bill McCreary]]\n|\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Ulf R\u00f6nnmark]]\n|{{flagicon|CAN}} [[Ray Scapinello]]\n|-\n|[[Ice hockey at the 1994 Winter Olympics|1994]]<br />\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Rob Hearn]]\n|\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Jay Borman]]\n|{{flagicon|CZE}} [[V\u00e1clav \u010cesk\u00fd]]\n|-\n|[[Ice hockey at the 1992 Winter Olympics|1992]]<br />\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Sven-Erik Sold]]\n|\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Johan Enestedt]]\n|{{flagicon|FIN}} [[Janne Rautavuori]]\n|-\n|[[Ice hockey at the 1920 Winter Olympics|1920]]<br />\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Joseph McCormick (ice hockey)|Joseph McCormick]]\n|\n|\n|\n|}\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Ice hockey|Olympics}}\n*[[List of Olympic venues in ice hockey]]\n*[[Ice sledge hockey at the Winter Paralympics]]\n\n==Notes==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==References==\n{{Refbegin|30em}}\n*{{Cite book|last=Judd|first=Ron C.|title=The Winter Olympics: An Insider's Guide to the Legends, the Lore and the Games|year=2008|edition=Vancouver|publisher=[[The Mountaineers (club)|The Mountaineers Books]]|location=Seattle|isbn=1-59485-063-1|ref=harv|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/winterolympicsin0000judd}}\n*{{Cite book|author=Kennedy Jr.|first=John F. |authorlink=John F. Kennedy Jr.|editor1-last=Findling|editor1-first=John E.|editor2-last=Pelle |editor2-first=Kimberly, D| chapter=Innsbruck 1976|title=Encyclopedia of the modern Olympic movement|edition=illustrated, revised|url=https://books.google.com/?id=QmXi_-Jujj0C&printsec=frontcover&dq=Encyclopedia+of+the+modern+Olympic+movement#PPA367,M1|publisher=[[Greenwood Publishing Group]]|year=2004|isbn=0-313-32278-3|ref=harv}}\n*{{Cite book|author=Morales|first=Yves|editor1-last=Findling|editor1-first=John E.|editor2-last=Pelle |editor2-first=Kimberly, D| ch